<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>Java - Tag - 编程心语</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/tags/java/</link><description>Java - Tag - 编程心语</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.ithome.me/tags/java/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>2024 05 22 Springboot2.5.9升级到springboot3.2.3</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2024/05/22/springboot2.5.9%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%B0springboot3.2/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>Simon</author><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2024/05/22/springboot2.5.9%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E5%88%B0springboot3.2/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h2 id="升级背景">升级背景</h2>
<p>Spring Boot 3.x 是一个重大版本升级，基于 Spring Framework 6，要求：</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Java 17+</strong>（最低要求）</li>
<li>Jakarta EE 9+（包名从 <code>javax.*</code> 迁移到 <code>jakarta.*</code>）</li>
<li>很多废弃的 API 被移除</li>
</ul>
<p>本文记录从 Spring Boot 2.5.9 升级到 3.2.3 的完整过程。</p>]]></description></item><item><title>2023 05 31 设计模式之单例模式</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2023/05/31/%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E4%B9%8B%E5%8D%95%E4%BE%8B%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 31 May 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>Simon</author><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2023/05/31/%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E4%B9%8B%E5%8D%95%E4%BE%8B%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h2 id="什么是单例模式">什么是单例模式</h2>
<p>单例模式（Singleton Pattern）是最常用的设计模式之一，它保证一个类只有一个实例，并提供一个全局访问点。</p>
<p>在实际开发中，单例模式常用于：</p>
<ul>
<li>数据库连接池</li>
<li>线程池</li>
<li>配置管理器</li>
<li>日志记录器</li>
</ul>]]></description></item><item><title>Java集合</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2020/04/23/java%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88/</link><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>Simon</author><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2020/04/23/java%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Java引用类型</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2020/04/20/java%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B/</link><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>Simon</author><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2020/04/20/java%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>JVM学习记录(一)</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2020/04/17/jvm%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%80/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>Simon</author><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2020/04/17/jvm%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%80/</guid><description>JVM思维导图</description></item><item><title>Java常见面试题</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2019/12/05/java%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%9D%A2%E8%AF%95%E9%A2%98/</link><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>Simon Chen</author><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2019/12/05/java%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%9D%A2%E8%AF%95%E9%A2%98/</guid><description>作者：SnailClimb 链接：https://juejin.im/post/5dba72c96fb9a02047526331 来源：掘金 著作</description></item><item><title>[转]Google Java编程风格指南</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2014/12/03/%E8%BD%ACgoogle-java%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</link><pubDate>Wed, 03 Dec 2014 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>Simon Chen</author><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2014/12/03/%E8%BD%ACgoogle-java%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</guid><description>作者：Hawstein 出处：[http://hawstein.com/posts/google-java-style.html](http:</description></item><item><title>android知识点之【java集合】</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2014/08/09/android%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%